OL,3,CNHS home births suspended across
OL,4,CGloucestershire
OL,6,FNHS home births have been suspended
OL,7,Facross Gloucestershire, after safety
OL,8,Fconcerns were raised by staff.
OL,10,FThe Gloucestershire Hospitals NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust says it will
OL,12,Finitially pause home births for two
OL,13,Fweeks, but it's possible this could
OL,14,Flead to a "longer suspension," as it
OL,15,Ftackles staffing difficulties.
OL,17,FBosses have apologised for the
OL,18,Fsuspension and say they're supporting
OL,19,Fwomen and families who had planned to
OL,20,Fgive birth at home.
