OL,3,CNHS home births suspended across
OL,4,CGloucestershire
OL,6,FHome births account for less than two
OL,7,Fper cent of births in the county, but
OL,8,Fthe trust says it's struggling to
OL,9,Fcover its on-call service at night.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Home births are intended for low-risk
OL,13,Fdeliveries, but when complications
OL,14,Farise, it can become unsafe for both
OL,15,Fmother and baby.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
