OL,6,F"During this pause, we are working on
OL,7,Fa risk assessment and options to find
OL,8,Fa balance between supporting choices
OL,9,Ffor giving birth and managing the
OL,10,Fstaffing levels to maintain safe care
OL,11,Facross the whole maternity service."
OL,13,FWhy has this decision been taken?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
