OL,3,CNHS home births suspended across
OL,4,CGloucestershire
OL,6,F"Over the past two years we have been
OL,7,Fable to recruit more midwives to our
OL,8,Fmain service, however, we have not yet
OL,9,Fbeen able to increase our home birth
OL,10,Fteams, which require significant
OL,11,Fskills and experience because of the
OL,12,Fdegree of autonomy they require to
OL,13,Fsupport a woman at home during
OL,14,Flabour," the trust added.
OL,16,F"Our team of community midwives will
OL,17,Fcontinue to provide antenatal care in
OL,18,Fthe community and midwife-led care
OL,19,Fwill continue to be provided at Stroud
OL,20,FMaternity Hospital and Gloucester
OL,21,FBirth Unit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
