OL,3,CNHS home births suspended across
OL,4,CGloucestershire
OL,6,F"We have already contacted women and
OL,7,Ffamilies who have told us they planned
OL,8,Fto give birth at home during this
OL,9,Ftime, and our midwives have talked
OL,10,Fthrough the options with them
OL,11,Findividually.
OL,13,F"We know this will be disappointing
OL,14,Ffor those who were planning a home
OL,15,Fbirth, and we are sorry that this is
OL,16,Fnot possible at this time.
OL,18,F"Our focus is always on ensuring the
OL,19,Fsafety of our services and at times
OL,20,Fthis means difficult decisions about
OL,21,Fwhere and how we provide care.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
