OL,6,F"If women or families want to discuss
OL,7,Ftheir plans, they can contact their
OL,8,Fmidwife as normal, who will be able to
OL,9,Fanswer any questions and talk about
OL,10,Fchoices.
OL,12,F"Our team of midwives and maternity
OL,13,Fsupport workers will continue to
OL,14,Fprovide families with the same level
OL,15,Fof midwife-led care and support at
OL,16,FGloucestershire Royal Hospital and
OL,17,FStroud Maternity Hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
